    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Through dialogue, we come into contact with the paranormal.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a counselor at a facility for children with hidden paranormal abilities.<br>You must fill in the chart with dialogue and observation within the limited time of 60 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/c29bf305a2244f5c84b6dc4e973b377c.poster.avif?t=1763694184\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/c29bf305a2244f5c84b6dc4e973b377c.webm?t=1763694184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/c29bf305a2244f5c84b6dc4e973b377c.mp4?t=1763694184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Children with various different paranormal abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most important thing you need to find out is the details of their hidden &quot;paranormal abilities.&quot; <br>We need to know what abilities they have, what triggers them to manifest, and how to deal with them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, the children you counsel are unique and challenging to work with.<br>Observe them and communicate with them to see which approaches work the best.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/e205cd82cd8e1a19a7c9d5d0e40cd426.poster.avif?t=1763694184\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/e205cd82cd8e1a19a7c9d5d0e40cd426.webm?t=1763694184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/e205cd82cd8e1a19a7c9d5d0e40cd426.mp4?t=1763694184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Point-and-click conversation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a point-and-click format. <br>You can communicate with them by using what is in the room or what they are wearing as conversation starters and by making choices that come up in the conversation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more trust you gain from them, the more in-depth information you may learn. <br>Conversely, if they are ever alarmed by you, your sanity will be at risk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/a85c5a3afac9976c11757142f82f5138.poster.avif?t=1763694184\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/a85c5a3afac9976c11757142f82f5138.webm?t=1763694184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/a85c5a3afac9976c11757142f82f5138.mp4?t=1763694184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your understanding will change the outcome</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more information you acquire and the more you fill out your medical records, the higher your reputation as a counselor will be. <br>Aim to be a better counselor. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's hope you don't run away during the process...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/4ad2b99851a3d5b0531b6cd564bdd14a.poster.avif?t=1763694184\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/4ad2b99851a3d5b0531b6cd564bdd14a.webm?t=1763694184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207350/extras/4ad2b99851a3d5b0531b6cd564bdd14a.mp4?t=1763694184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
